item.title: Reply Cyber Security Challenge 2020 Write-ups
item.description: A few days ago on 09/10/2020 Reply held yet another Cyber Security challenge on their site. It was a jeopardy style CTF with 25 flags spread across 5 different categories and 24 hours to find them. The prizes for the competition looked great so my team and I registered immediately hoping for the best. We had seen past challenges that they’d organized and our hopes were really high. Anyway, this is my write-up for the challenges I managed to complete during the competition.
